foobarf00 writes "[0]LinRails is a binary package that includes
Ruby-1.8.6, Rubygems-0.9.4, Rails 1.2.3, Mongrel 1.0.1, MySQL-5.0.41,
ncurses-5.6, OpenSSL-0.9.8e, and zlib-1.2.3. Its goal is to make it easy
